 <ul>
  <li><%= link_to "Forums", general_help_path('discussions', 'forums') %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Topics", general_help_path('discussions', 'topics') %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Posts", general_help_path('discussions', 'posts') %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Moderators", general_help_path('discussions', 'moderators') %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Monitoring", general_help_path('discussions', 'monitoring') %></li>
 </ul>
 <hr/>
 <h2>Other Questions?</h2>
 <p>If there is something else you want to ask about the posts from a discussion group participant, try the <%= link_to "help forums", forums_path('help') %> for Little<span class='company'>Red</span>Brick tech support.</p>
</div>
